wdi2-TM.TAX.MANF.IP.ZS.def: Share of tariff lines with international peaks is the share of lines in the tariff schedule with tariff rates that exceed 15 percent. Manufactured products are commodities classified in SITC revision 3 sections 5-8 excluding division 68.
wdi2-TM.TAX.MANF.IP.ZS.name: Share of tariff lines with international peaks
wdi2-TM.TAX.MANF.IP.ZS.source: World Bank staff estimates using the World Integrated Trade Solution system, based on data from United Nations Conference on Trade and Development's Trade Analysis and Information System (TRAINS) database.
